info.author: David Dalisay & Christian Lowe
info.description:
# SchedulerBot
A simple Discord bot that allows everyone on a server to create scheduled gaming events. This bot will help gamers with scheduling group gaming sessions at certain times.
info.name: SchedulerBot
info.summary: A Discord Bot that helps you schedule gaming events with your friends.
